# WINET Lab Website Project Overview

This is the official website for the Wireless Intelligence and Networked Things Laboratory (WINET) at City University of Hong Kong, led by Prof. Yuguang "Michael" Fang.

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend**: Vanilla HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)
- **Dependencies**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Front-matter parser, Glob file matching
- **Styling**: Custom CSS with Font Awesome 6.4.0 icons, Google Fonts (Inter family)
- **Data Format**: JSON for research data, Markdown with YAML front-matter for content
- **Build System**: Static website with dynamic content loading via JavaScript

## Core Architecture Files
- [index.html](mdc:index.html): Main entry point with slideshow, navigation, and dynamic content sections
- [styles.css](mdc:styles.css): Global styles with responsive design and section-specific styling
- [script.js](mdc:script.js): Main JavaScript with slideshow functionality and navigation
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and metadata

