## Data Organization Patterns

### Team Member Structure
Each member directory under `/data/people/` contains:
- `_index.md`: Profile with YAML front-matter and Markdown content
- `avatar.png`: Profile photo (recommended: 400x400px minimum)
- Optional: Additional files (CV, publications, etc.)

### Seminar Structure
Each seminar directory under `/data/seminar/` contains:
- `index.md`: Seminar details with YAML front-matter
- `index.html`: Generated HTML content
- `featured.jpg`: Speaker photo or event image
- Optional: Presentation slides, additional materials

### Research Areas Structure
- **Data Source**: [data/research.json](mdc:data/research.json) contains hierarchical research data
- **Static Pages**: Each major research area has a dedicated static HTML page in `/pages/`
- **Navigation**: Main page dynamically loads research areas and links to static detail pages
- **Page Mapping**: Defined in [index.html](mdc:index.html) JavaScript for category-to-page routing

